trans-unit.source: Represents an entry in either back or forward navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Reprezentuje wpis w historii przeglądania do przodu lub Wstecz.

trans-unit.source: [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-wpf-md.md)] implements a navigation history service that stores one entry for each piece of content that has been previously navigated to, just like navigation history in [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-wpf-md.md)]implementuje usługi historii nawigacji, która przechowuje jeden wpis dla każdego z nich zawartości, która została wcześniej nawigację, podobnie jak w historii nawigacji w [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Navigation history comprises two stacks, one that remembers back navigation history, and one that remembers forward navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Historii nawigacji składa się z dwóch stosy, który są przechowywane dane historii nawigacji Wstecz i jednego pamięta historii przeglądania do przodu.

trans-unit.source: An entry for the current item is added to back navigation history when a forward navigation occurs.
trans-unit.target: Wpis dla bieżącego elementu zostanie dodane do kopii historii przeglądania podczas nawigacji do przodu.

trans-unit.source: This occurs in the following situations: - The `Navigate` method is called (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).
trans-unit.target: Dzieje się tak w następujących sytuacjach: - `Navigate` metoda jest wywoływana (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - The `GoForward` method is called (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).
trans-unit.target: - `GoForward` Metoda jest wywoływana (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - The forward button on the navigation [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] that is displayed from the current navigator ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).
trans-unit.target: -Przycisk Prześlij dalej w nawigacji [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] która jest wyświetlana z bieżącym Nawigatora ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: Likewise, an entry for the current item is added to forward navigation history before a back navigation occurs, which happens when: - The `GoBack` method is called (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).
trans-unit.target: Podobnie, dodać wpis dla bieżącego elementu w historii przeglądania do przodu przed wystąpieniem nawigacji Wstecz, które się stanie, gdy: - `GoBack` metoda jest wywoływana (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - The back button on the navigation [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] that is displayed from the current navigator ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).
trans-unit.target: -Przycisku Wstecz w nawigacji [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] która jest wyświetlana z bieżącym Nawigatora ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: Each entry in back and forward navigation history is an instance of the JournalEntry class.
trans-unit.target: Każdy wpis na spód i historii przeglądania do przodu jest wystąpienie klasy JournalEntry.

trans-unit.source: Each JournalEntry object encapsulates information about a particular navigation, including a name for the entry (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Name%2A>), whether the entry is kept alive (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.KeepAlive%2A>) and the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] for the content that is navigated to (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Source%2A>).
trans-unit.target: Każdy obiekt JournalEntry hermetyzuje informacje dotyczące konkretnego nawigacji, w tym nazwę wpisu (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Name%2A>), czy wpis jest aktywne (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.KeepAlive%2A>) i [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] dla zawartości, która jest przejście (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Source%2A>).</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Source%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.KeepAlive%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Name%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can retrieve all the JournalEntry objects in back navigation history by enumerating the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties.
trans-unit.target: Możesz pobrać wszystkie obiekty JournalEntry w historii nawigacji Wstecz wyliczania <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>lub <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>Właściwości.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For forward navigation history, you can retrieve all the JournalEntry objects by enumerating the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties.
trans-unit.target: Historii przeglądania do przodu, możesz pobrać wszystkie obiekty JournalEntry wyliczania <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>lub <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>Właściwości.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If you need to remove the most recent JournalEntry object from back navigation history, to prevent navigation to it, for example, you can call the `RemoveBackEntry` method (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>), which removes the JournalEntry object and returns a reference to it.
trans-unit.target: Jeśli musisz usunąć ostatniego obiektu JournalEntry z historii nawigacji Wstecz, aby zapobiec nawigacji, na przykład można wywołać `RemoveBackEntry` — metoda (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>), które usuwa obiekt JournalEntry i zwraca odwołanie do niego</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: You cannot add JournalEntry objects to navigation history, however, because you can neither instantiate nor derive from JournalEntry, and because no type implements a member to do so.
trans-unit.target: Nie można dodać obiektów JournalEntry do historii nawigacji, ponieważ nie można utworzyć wystąpienia ani pochodzić od JournalEntry, a nie typ implementuje element członkowski, aby to zrobić.

trans-unit.source: However, you can add custom <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> objects to back navigation history by calling the `AddBackEntry` method (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.AddBackEntry%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.AddBackEntry%2A>); <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService> adds the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> object to an internally-created JournalEntry object, which is then added to the back navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Można jednak dodać niestandardowe obiekty <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>kopii historii nawigacji przez wywołanie metody `AddBackEntry` — metoda (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.AddBackEntry%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.AddBackEntry%2A>); <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService>dodaje <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>obiektu do obiektu JournalEntry utworzone wewnętrznie, która jest następnie dodawana do historii przeglądania do tyłu.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.AddBackEntry%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.AddBackEntry%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>
